        "bullet_point": {
            "value": [
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "SAND SCOOP FOR METAL DETECTING - The ASR Outdoor sand sifter digger trrowel is an essential accessory for metal detecting. It measures 9\" in length and has a 6\" wide mouth so you can easily remove rocks and sand while searching for treasure on the beach",
                    "marketplace_id": "ATVPDKIKX0DER"
                },
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "78 HOLES PER SCOOP - The plastic sand scoop features 78 holes, each with a diameter of 0.50\". These holes will assist you with removing dirt and sand while locating your treasure on the beach or river bed",
                    "marketplace_id": "ATVPDKIKX0DER"
                },
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "HEAVY DUTY PLASTIC SAND SCOOP - Constructed from reinforced, heavy-duty single piecemolded ABS plastic, the sand scoop is durable and will not rust or corrode so you can use it in any weather. Since it's made of plastic, you won't have to worry about any false positives while metal detecting",
                    "marketplace_id": "ATVPDKIKX0DER"
                },
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "ULTRA-LIGHTWEIGHT DESIGN - The beach sifting scoop weighs just 0.50 pounds (8 ounces) making it easy to use for both kids and adults. It will fit inside most standard-sized backpacks and won't add too much to your carry weight",
                    "marketplace_id": "ATVPDKIKX0DER"
                },
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "SPECIFICATIONS - Dimensions: 9\" x 6\" x 5.5\"; Capacity: 3 Quarts; Material: Single Construction Durable Plastic; Color: Green; Holes per Scoop: 78, Hole Diameter: .5\"",
